File: cmd/gophkeeper/main.go
Package: main
Scope: Exported
Role: Entrypoint
Purpose: Initializes client configuration and executes the root CLI command tree. Separates execution logic into run function for testability.

Functions:
func main(). Purpose: Entrypoint flow. Invokes run and logs fatal error on failure.
func run() error. Purpose: Operational logic. Initializes Viper config via config.NewViper, constructs client root command tree via commands.NewRootCommand, and triggers arguments parsing via cmd.Execute. Errors: returns wrapped initialization or command execution errors.
